        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 19. Scanning electron micrographs of polyp sclerites of Ovabunda macrospiculata (Gohar, 1940) paratype (ZMTAU Co 35791). a Regular sclerite b Irregular sclerites c Fused sclerites. Arrows indicate surface dents. Scale bar 10 µm." , "Figure 18. Scanning electron micrographs of polyp sclerites of Ovabunda macrospiculata (Gohar, 1940) paratype (ZMTAU Co 35790). a Regular sclerites b Irregular sclerite c Fused sclerites d Pear-shaped sclerite. Scale bar 10 µm." , "Figure 17. Scanning electron micrographs of polyp sclerites of Ovabunda macrospiculata (Gohar, 1940) neotype (ZMTAU Co 25635). a Pear-shape sclerite b Regular sclerites c Fused sclerite. Scale bar 10 µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/22454" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/22453" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/22452" .

